data.description: Beautifully kept home South I10 in Crestview! This home features updated flooring downstairs, granite countertops, white cabinetry, and a well sized backyard! This home offers 3 large bedrooms, one with on suite bathroom which has double sinks, soaker tub, shower, and walk in closet! Downstairs features living, dining, bonus room, half bathroom, and sunroom area!Schedule a showing today!
